                  </div>
                  <div style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace;color:#5a7090;font-size:1.0rem;
                    letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-top:8px;">
                    Avg RMSE = {avg_rmse*1000:.2f} mV &nbsp;|&nbsp;
